{"id":686492,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/686492.html","date":"2022-09-03T19:53:35Z","modified":"2022-09-03T19:53:35Z","title":"【CDTV】中国多地使用无人机在居民楼外巡逻并进行防疫宣传","content":"<div style=\"width:100%;margin:0 auto;padding-left:20px\">\n<div class=\"su-spoiler su-spoiler-style-fancy su-spoiler-icon-chevron-circle su-spoiler-closed\" data-scroll-offset=\"0\" data-anchor-in-url=\"no\"><div class=\"su-spoiler-title\" tabindex=\"0\" role=\"button\"><span class=\"su-spoiler-icon\"></span>CDT 档案卡</div><div class=\"su-spoiler-content su-u-clearfix su-u-trim\">\n<strong>标题：</strong>【CDTV】中国多地使用无人机在居民楼外巡逻并进行防疫宣传<br />\n<strong>来源：</strong>推特账号@Songpinganq、抖音用户@34986297760（原作者不详）<br />\n<strong>发表日期：</strong>2022.9.3<br />\n<strong>主题归类：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/tag/%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%BA%E6%9C%BA%E9%98%B2%E7%96%AB\" target=\"_blank\">无人机防疫</a><br>\n<strong>CDS收藏：</strong><a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/space/%E5%85%AC%E6%B0%91%E9%A6%86\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">公民馆</a><br>\n<strong>版权说明：</strong>该作品版权归原作者所有。中国数字时代仅对原作进行存档，以对抗中国的网络审查。<a href=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/copyright\">详细版权说明</a>。\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<p>随着中国多个城市新冠疫情再次爆发，当局使用了更严苛的疫情防控手段，其中多地都出现了无人机在居民楼外巡逻并进行防疫宣传的情况。</p>\n<p>8月17日，江苏省无锡市，一架无人机在居民楼外进行巡逻宣传：</p>\n<blockquote><p>\n疫情防控通知内容，严格执行居家隔离措施，做到人不出区，错峰进入，请广大居民群众，切实履行个人防疫责任\n</p></blockquote>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.8.17 江苏省无锡市居民楼外无人机巡逻并进行防疫宣传\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/AztqqANMBPE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>8月30日，四川省成都市，也发生了类似事件，一架无人机在小区内进行防疫宣传：</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.8.30 成都市居民楼外无人机巡逻并进行防疫宣传\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/Jt5aKnoTzq4?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>8月31日，山西省晋城市，一架无人机在居民区内进行全面消杀，根据视频配文，该小区已经被封6天：</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.8.31 山西省晋城市无人机在居民区内进行消杀\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/e-5t6xssA6w?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>9月1日，海南省某居民区，当局还使用无人机要求居民下楼做核酸：</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.9.1 海南居民楼外无人机巡逻并进行防疫宣传\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/GWAjTSoJjBE?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n<p>9月3日，湖北省孝感市某居民区外，也出现了当局使用无人机进行防疫宣传的情况：</p>\n<p><iframe loading=\"lazy\" title=\"2022.9.3 湖北省孝感市居民楼外无人机巡逻并进行防疫宣传\" width=\"1080\" height=\"608\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/vrb1tfxjgIg?feature=oembed\" frameborder=\"0\" allow=\"accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture\" allowfullscreen></iframe></p>\n","author":1092,"categories":[45870,41492,43134,45438,45443,38927],"tags":[29203,39890,45283,45826,39920]}